description: Adler slicer Adler AD 4701 Now you can even have transparent slices How to get perfectly even slices? The slicer will do it for us. We choose the cutting depth ourselves, which is very easy thanks to a clear indication of the current thickness setting. It has 5 temperatures to choose from, from 40-98°C, and it automatically re-heats the water to keep it at a constant temperature. It’s so easy to fill, keeps water at your chosen temperature and dispenses without the danger of scalding. A stylish addition to any kitchen, the Thermo Pot has a coated stainless steel thermal casing that never gets too hot to touch.
